[
    {
        "id": "4cd008773e23b584",
        "type": "tab",
        "label": "Plant Watering System",
        "disabled": false,
        "info": "Automated Desk Plant Watering System \u2014 ELT2720\nGPIO assignments (verified against schematic):\n  SPILL_IN    GPIO17  pin 11\n  LED_STATUS  GPIO23  pin 16\n  MAN_BUTTON  GPIO25  pin 22\n  I2C_SDA     GPIO2   pin 3\n  I2C_SCL     GPIO3   pin 5\n  TRIG        GPIO5   pin 29\n  ECHO        GPIO6   pin 31\n  PUMP_GATE   GPIO12  pin 32\n\nflowsVersion: flows-13 (fixes: poll-sync water+soil, LCD low-water state,\n  pump_running deadlock on redeploy, gate wired from cistern output)\n\nRequired packages (install in ~/.node-red):\n  npm install node-red-contrib-cistern\n  npm install node-red-contrib-i2c\n\nCistern: radius=12.5cm, maxDistance=20cm, minDistance=3cm\n\nLCD via PCF8574 (0x27):\n  RS=0x01  EN=0x04  BL=0x08\n  D4=0x10  D5=0x20  D6=0x40  D7=0x80"
    },
